# 📚 PersonalLearningPro – AI-Powered Personalized Learning Platform

> Revolutionizing education through adaptive, intelligent, and personalized learning experiences powered by AI.

---

## 🎯 Overview

**PersonalLearningPro** is a full-stack web application designed to deliver tailored educational content using AI. It customizes learning experiences based on each student's pace, style, and performance using dynamic quiz generation and feedback systems.

---

## 🌟 Key Features

- 🎓 **Adaptive Learning Paths** – Adjusts to the user's learning pace and style.
- 💬 **AI-Generated Questions** – Uses OpenAI (GPT) to create dynamic and context-aware quizzes.
- 📊 **Progress Tracking** – Visual dashboards for learners and educators.
- 👨‍🏫 **Teacher & Student Portals** – Separate interfaces for managing and analyzing learning.
- 🔒 **Secure Authentication** – User registration, login, and role-based access.

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Layer         | Technology                        |
|---------------|------------------------------------|
| Frontend      | React.js, Tailwind CSS, Vite       |
| Backend       | Node.js, Express.js, TypeScript    |
| AI Integration| OpenAI GPT API                     |
| Database      | Firebase or MongoDB                |
| Hosting       | Vercel (Frontend), Render (Backend)|
| Dev Tools     | Git, VS Code, Postman              |

---

## 🚀 Getting Started

### 🔧 Prerequisites
- Node.js >= 18
- Git
- OpenAI API key (for GPT features)

### 📦 Installation

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/<your-username>/PersonalLearningPro.git
cd PersonalLearningPro

# Install dependencies
npm install

# Run development server
npm run dev




 Then visit: http://localhost:5000
